taot (0.2.1) unstable; urgency=low
  * Support for language swap.
  * Yandex.Translate: Fixed SSL handshake error due to a missing CA
    certificate.
  * Yandex.Translate: Added error handling.
  * Yandex.Translate: Sort languages by name.

